                        <interp inst="t18680706-636-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted, to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY.**</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18680706-636-punishment-70" type="punishmentDescription">
