                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-636-18680706 t18680706-636-punishment-70"></join>Seven Years' Penal Servitude. Twelve other con<lb></lb>victions were proved against the prisoner</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
